If you are familiar with baked eggs or are a fan of the saying, “eat breakfast like a king”, then this recipe is for you. Take baked eggs to the next level by adding a sweet potato and cheese base for the most delicious, satisfying, savoury breakfast you’ll eat yet. And, the best part? It’s ready in 25 minutes. *Recipe makes 8 egg cups. Sweet potato hash egg cups. Photo: Taste of Home